<section id="how-to" class="sus-section">
    <div class="sus-content">
        <h2 class="sus-heading">Learn how to be sustainable</h2>
        <p class="sus-desc">
            Sustainability isn’t just about saving the planet. It’s about living
            thoughtfully, being considerate, and looking after yourself.
        </p>

        <ul class="sus-list">
            <li>
                <span class="number">01</span>
                <span class="text"
                    >Reduce, reuse, recycle and repair : “The four R’s”.
                </span>
            </li>
            <li>
                <span class="number">02</span>
                <span class="text"
                    >Shop consciously, Eat mindfully, Choose the right
                    transportation.</span
                >
            </li>
            <li>
                <span class="number">03</span>
                <span class="text"
                    >Be careful with your energy use, Conserve water.</span
                >
            </li>
            <li>
                <span class="number">04</span>
                <span class="text"
                    >Understand what sustainability means, Support green
                    initiatives.</span
                >
            </li>
        </ul>

        <a href="#" class="sus-btn">Discover More</a>
    </div>

    <div class="sus-image">
        <div class="image-box"></div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .sus-section {
        display: flex;
        gap: 60px;
        align-items: center;
        padding: 0 var(--page-padding-horizontal);
        margin-top: 60px;
    }

    .sus-content {
        flex: 1;
    }

    .sus-heading {
        margin-top: 0;
        font-family: font1;
        font-size: var(--font-size-heading);
        margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .sus-desc {
        font-family: font2;
        color: var(--text-paragraph);
        margin-bottom: 40px;
    }

    .sus-list {
        list-style: none;
        padding: 0;
        margin-bottom: 40px;
    }

    .sus-list li {
        display: flex;
        align-items: flex-start;
        padding: 20px 0;
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--divider-color);
        font-family: font2;
    }

    .sus-list li:first-child {
        border-top: 1px solid var(--divider-color);
    }

    .number {
        font-weight: bold;
        margin-right: 20px;
        min-width: 30px;
    }

    .sus-btn {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 14px 28px;
        background-color: var(--accent2);
        color: var(--text-headline);
        border-radius: 100px;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-family: font2;
        font-weight: bold;
    }

    .sus-btn:hover {
        background-color: var(--accent3);
        color: var(--accent2);
    }

    .sus-image {
        flex: 1;
        height: 500px;
        background-color: #cdbe9e; /* Beige color from design */
        border-radius: 30px;
        overflow: hidden;
    }

    .image-box {
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        /* background-image: url("logo.svg"); */
        background-size: cover;
        background-position: center;
    }

    @media (max-width: 900px) {
        .sus-section {
            flex-direction: column;
        }
        .sus-image {
            width: 100%;
            height: 400px;
        }
    }
</style>
